name: Aesthoplasm s150604
description: Number s150604 of the Aesthoplasm series — Year: 2015 — Artist: Raphaël de Courville (@sableraph) — 60 frames at 500 × 500 pixels — This is one of the earliest pieces of the Aesthoplasm series. It is part of a small number of pieces that were created before Aesthoplasm became a daily sketch project in April 2017.
